---
description: Preserve core data integration flow and protection
globs: app/api/**/*.ts
alwaysApply: true
---

# Core Engine + Protection Guardrails

- Never remove or bypass the existing Google/Sheets/Drive integration flow in these routes:
  - `app/api/draft/route.ts` (GET/POST)
  - `app/api/submit/route.ts`
  - `app/api/registry/ensure/route.ts`
  - `app/api/_registrySheet.ts`
- Never remove or bypass `withGoogleApiRetry` usage.
  - When calling Google APIs (Sheets/Drive/permissions), the call must be wrapped by `withGoogleApiRetry(...)`.
  - Do not refactor these calls into unwrapped direct Google client calls.
- Do not change the request/response contract for these endpoints unless explicitly requested:
  - `/api/draft` (`ok`, `draft` payload)
  - `/api/pdf` (PDF generation inputs)
  - `/api/submit` (submit payload)
  - `/api/registry/ensure` (ensure login row)
- If a change risks touching these routes or their contracts, ask for confirmation before applying the edit.

